org.sensorhub.impl.persistence

Class InMemoryBasicStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sensorhub.impl.module.AbstractModule<StorageConfig>
      • org.sensorhub.impl.persistence.InMemoryBasicStorage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEventProducer, IModule<StorageConfig>, IBasicStorage<StorageConfig>, IStorageModule<StorageConfig>

    public class InMemoryBasicStorage
extends AbstractModule<StorageConfig>
implements IBasicStorage<StorageConfig>

    In-memory basic storage implementation. This is used mainly for test purposes but could perhaps be improved to be used as a local memory cache of a remote storage.
